// src/terminal/escape_types.npk — VT100/xterm escape sequence constants
//
// v0.2.0: Defines all control codes, parser states, and event type tags
// used by the VT parser state machine.
//
// Note: All constants are module-level variables. When imported via
// `use "escape_types.npk".*;` they become accessible in the importer.
//
// Reference: Paul Flo Williams' vt100.net DEC ANSI parser state diagram
//            ECMA-48 (control functions for coded character sets)

func:failsafe = int32(tbb32:err) { exit 1; };

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// C0 Control Codes (0x00–0x1F)
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

